0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dag0UD9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDag0UD9.jpg&h=ecaf5623&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ef4c6a86a83b301064dd6cb78747b03c15db38a","tid":893512,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/566zY5W.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F566zY5W.gif&h=2d5866e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adcebbe18651d537cbe6f5c5d962029241a2c419","tid":893512,"uid":212524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"好老實，最後果張肥果邊好睇d， 瘦咗反而好唔好睇"},{"pid":"15ff2853be8dcfbd353a35ee864a569a1018cdf5","tid":893512,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"adcebbe18651d537cbe6f5c5d962029241a2c419","tid":893512,"uid":212524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"好老實，最後果張肥果邊好睇d， 瘦咗反而好唔好睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"叫你屌呀唔係睇<br />\n定係你真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f27811671ca2cdfc9421f69de304da4c0d7e38","tid":893512,"uid":36911,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:53:13.000Z","msg":"個韓妹EX注定食唔到瘦左之後嘅佢<br />\n唔分手繼續食肥西,分手減完肥又冇佢份<br />\n<br />\nD女係要俾人飛先會有決心去減肥,真係以為一齊左就唔洗KEEP身型"},{"pid":"4fc0f2475d4db1bdb45803e1a071a717515a8235","tid":893512,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:59:19.000Z","msg":"肥先好睇"}]}